Re-usable FPGA Bitfile RPM Packager
-----------------------------------

A cmake build environment that, given an .rbf file and some paramters can generate an rpm.
Based on the Fiji cmake build environment.


========
Requires
========

cmake (2.8 or higher)
rpmbuild
subversion (1.8 or higher)


========
Usage
========

./generate.bash <rbf file> <top-level regmap .xml> <rpm prefix> <project name>

Example:

./generate.bash /build/buildbot.fpga/fijiNightly/build.2014-06-26.0000-01/projects/fiji/top/syn_best/fiji_top.rbf /build/buildbot.fpga/fijiNightly/build.2014-06-26.0000-01/projects/fiji/top/doc/fiji_regs_top.xml nas fiji

